data.title: FOE Reviewer
data.meta_description: FOE Reviewer - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides an overview of the scope and content covered in a fire officer examination. The specialized area section focuses on fire suppression and includes definitions of fire, fire tetrahedron, classes of fire A-K, classification of fire causes, pre-fire planning, firefighting techniques/procedures including basic firefighting divisions of pre-planning, size-up, rescue, and exposure. Key elements covered are the chemical process of combustion, components needed for fire, different types of fires/fuels, and standard firefighting procedures and strategies.
